---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken & Asian Veggie Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice
description: Say hello to your new dinner favourite! Tender chicken breast gets a savoury oyster sauce glaze, bringing bold umami flavours to every bite. Paired with vibrant green veggies and fluffy jasmine rice, this dish is a perfect balance of savoury, fresh, and comforting.

